Benoît-Constant Coquelin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beno%C3%AEt-Constant_Coquelin 0 Benoît-Constant Coquelin (French pronunciation: ​[bənwa kɔ̃stɑ̃ kɔklɛ̃]; 23 January 1841 – 27 January 1909), known as Coquelin aîné ("Coquelin the Elder"), was a French actor, "one of the greatest theatrical figures of the age."
